summary: Brand-New Lego Set Leaks Avengers Endgames Battles
body:
Brand-New Lego Set Leaks Avengers Endgames Battles

This Lego Set Seems To Leak One Of The Battles Somewhere From The Middle Of The Movie. I Cannot Show Pictures Due To Marvel And Lego Not Wanting It Spreading. If You Want To See It, Then Google It.

WARNING: POST CONTAINS SPOILERS FOR AVENGERS ENDGAME!

The Lego Set Shows Chitauri Attacking The Avengers Facility And Trying To Stop The Avengers From Entering The Quantum Realm. We See The New So Called “Thanos Buster” Which Seems To Be 2X The Size Of The Hulk Buster. And Ofcourse, Rhodey Is Wearing The Suit. The Chitauri Coming To Earth Might Be What The Avengers Were Looking At In The Sky At The Avengers Facility In The New Super Bowl Trailer. Also For Some Reason, There Are No Thanos Lego Minifigures For Endgame! Weird Isn’t It? More Details Coming
